Class ConfigAttributesNode

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class ConfigAttributesNode
extends ConfigKeyValueNode
    Configuration node representing attributes to be specified for a path node. Parameters are specified as key/value pairs enclosed in a {attributes} block for JSON and node attributes for XML.
